name: Space Boots
description: The year was 4321 Dusty the stampede wrote a song called "Space Boots" He then sent a signal to Mike Shinoda who produced the track on his Twitch channel. Then mumu_thestan created the cool cover art and gif for everyone to enjoy! All Tezos that Dusty receives from this collaboration are going straight back into his next release The Astronaut Vol. 2
